      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this motorcar in exemplary showroom condition. This vehicle has been curated to the highest standards, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in a state of absolute preservation. Meticulously maintained with an uncompromising attention to detail, this specimen offers a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer to acquire a vehicle of peerless quality and mechanical distinction.",
