    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014it basically looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super careful with it, keeping it pampered and garage-stored since day one. It drives like an absolute dream and has been meticulously cared for. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly loved and is ready for a new home, this is the one for you. I'd love for you to come by and see it for yourself!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
